OL,3,C13 year old girl appears in court over
OL,4,Cschool stabbing
OL,6,FA 13 year old girl has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt for the first time charged with
OL,8,Fattempted murder after a stabbing at a
OL,9,Fschool in west Wales.
OL,11,FPupils at Amman Valley School, also
OL,12,Fknown as Ysgol Dyffryn Aman, in went
OL,13,Finto lockdown just after 11.20am on
OL,14,FWednesday after the stabbing at the
OL,15,Fend of morning break.
OL,17,FTwo teachers and a pupil were hurt in
OL,18,Fthe incident but have since been
OL,19,Freleased from hospital.
