OL,3,C13 year old girl appears in court over
OL,4,Cschool stabbing
OL,6,FShe was remanded to a youth detention
OL,7,Faccommodation.
OL,9,FDistrict Judge Mark Layton said
OL,10,Fremanding a 13-year-old into youth
OL,11,Fjustice detention was a "difficult
OL,12,Fdecision" in a hearing that lasted
OL,13,Faround 20 minutes.
OL,15,FLaura Sherwood, representing the girl,
OL,16,Fmade an application for bail which was
OL,17,Frefused by the judge.
OL,19,FAbigail Jackson appeared for the
OL,20,Fprosecution
