OL,3,C13 year old girl appears in court over
OL,4,Cschool stabbing
OL,6,FIt comes as a 15-year-old boy was
OL,7,Farrested later on Wednesday after
OL,8,Fpolice received reports about messages
OL,9,Fon social media referring to the
OL,10,Fstabbing.
OL,12,FOne of the teachers injured in the
OL,13,Fattack has been named as Fiona Elias,
OL,14,Fthe head of year seven.
OL,16,FThe second adult is reported to be Liz
OL,17,FHopkin, a special needs teacher.
