OL,3,C13 year old girl appears in court over
OL,4,Cschool stabbing
OL,6,FThe south-west Wales school went into
OL,7,Flockdown after a "code red" alarm
OL,8,Fsounded through the PA system, during
OL,9,Fwhich students and staff are said to
OL,10,Fhave hidden in classrooms ` with one
OL,11,Fpupil reportedly vaulting the school
OL,12,Ffence to get to safety.
OL,14,FThe lockdown lasted around four hours
OL,15,Fbetween 11.20am and 3.20pm, resulting
OL,16,Fin a lengthy and anxious wait for
OL,17,Fparents who were seen tearfully
OL,18,Fhugging their children after they
OL,19,Fwalked through the gates.
